    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine your <strong>vegan</strong> <strong>mayo</strong>, <strong>ketchup</strong> and <strong>mustard ketchup </strong>in a small bowl – this is your <strong>special sauce</strong></p>",
