    {
      "instruction": "<p>To assemble, spread the <strong>special sauce </strong>on the <strong>brioche base</strong>, then top with a <strong>cheezy meat-free patty</strong>, a sprinkling of your <strong>crispy onions </strong>and a <strong>brioche lid</strong> – this is your<strong> American plant-based cheezeburger</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>potato wedges </strong>and<strong> quick-pickled cucumber wedges</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
